---
import MainLayout from '../../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
import CTA from '../../components/CTA.astro';

// 1. Import the Astro Image component and your specific image
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import cataractImg from '../../assets/cataract.png';

// SEO Optimized Meta Data
const pageTitle = "Advanced Stitchless Cataract Surgery in Chennai";
const pageDescription = "Restore crystal-clear vision with painless, stitchless cataract surgery and premium IOLs by AIIMS-trained specialists in KK Nagar. Schedule a consultation.";
---

<MainLayout title={pageTitle} description={pageDescription}>
  <section class="bg-blue-900 text-white py-20 px-6">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-12">
      <div class="md:w-1/2">
        <span class="text-blue-300 font-bold tracking-wider uppercase text-sm mb-4 block">Surgical Excellence</span>
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold mb-6 leading-tight">Advanced Cataract Surgery & Premium IOLs</h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-blue-100 mb-8 leading-relaxed">
          Restore crystal-clear vision with stitchless, painless phacoemulsification performed by an AIIMS-trained specialist.
        </p>
        <a href="#book" class="bg-white text-blue-900 font-bold px-8 py-3 rounded-md shadow-lg hover:bg-blue-50 transition inline-block">Book an Evaluation</a>
      </div>
      <div class="md:w-1/2 w-full">
        <Image 
          src={cataractImg} 
          alt="Premium Intraocular Lens for Cataract Surgery" 
          class="rounded-2xl shadow-2xl border-4 border-white/10 w-full object-cover aspect-video" 
        />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 px-6 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
    <div class="prose prose-lg prose-blue max-w-none text-slate-700">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-blue-900 mb-6">What is a Cataract?</h2>
      <p class="mb-6">
        A cataract is the clouding of the eye’s natural lens, which lies behind the iris and the pupil. It is a normal part of aging, but it can lead to a progressive decrease in vision. If you are experiencing glare from headlights at night, needing brighter light to read, or feeling like you are looking through a frosty or fogged-up window, a cataract may be forming.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-blue-900 mt-12 mb-6">Our Approach: Micro-Incision Phacoemulsification</h2>
      <p class="mb-6">
        At Crispr Eye Care, we utilize state-of-the-art <strong>phacoemulsification technology</strong>. This advanced procedure uses ultrasound energy to gently break up the cloudy lens, which is then carefully removed through a microscopic incision. 
      </p>
      
      <div class="bg-blue-50 p-8 rounded-xl border border-blue-100 my-10">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-blue-900 mb-4">Benefits of our Surgical Technique:</h3>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 font-medium">
          <li><strong>No Stitches or Injections:</strong> The micro-incision heals naturally without sutures.</li>
          <li><strong>Painless Procedure:</strong> Performed under topical anesthesia (eye drops).</li>
          <li><strong>Rapid Recovery:</strong> Most patients notice a dramatic improvement in vision within 24 hours.</li>
          <li><strong>Day-Care Surgery:</strong> Walk in, and walk out the same day.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-blue-900 mt-12 mb-6">Premium Intraocular Lenses (IOLs)</h2>
      <p class="mb-6">
        Once the cataract is removed, Dr. Rajeswari implants a pristine, artificial intraocular lens (IOL). We offer a range of premium lenses tailored to your lifestyle, including:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 mb-10">
        <li><strong>Monofocal IOLs:</strong> Excellent distance vision (reading glasses may be required).</li>
        <li><strong>Multifocal & Trifocal IOLs:</strong> Designed to provide clear vision at distance, intermediate, and near, reducing dependence on glasses.</li>
        <li><strong>Toric IOLs:</strong> Specifically designed to correct astigmatism during cataract surgery.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <CTA 
    title="Schedule Your Cataract Evaluation"
    address="39/2, R K Shanmugam Salai, K K Nagar, Chennai – 600078"
    phone="+91 63813 02828"
  />
</MainLayout>
